{"tid":817333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超強颱風逼港】天文台調高風勢預測：周日離岸吹10級暴風","createTime":"2018-09-13T10:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T11:13:39.000Z","uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6b321e8f1eac534ea10be162c77ee4a876f04e4b","tid":817333,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180913/58677701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58677701&d=fKS%2B8ftiISyyt3LDjTGZuAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d1602d1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58677701&h=9c50896c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180913/58677701</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台前晚原預計超強颱風「山竹」，最大機會在周日（16日）於尖沙嘴天文台總部西南方70公里左右掠過，可算是正面吹襲，但由於全球主流的氣象超級電腦，均南調山竹的預測路徑，天文台亦跟隨，改料山竹最大機會在本港西南200公里左右掠過。但由於山竹環流廣闊，加上預測時間縮短，天文台反而「調高」當日的風勢預測，除維持普遍地區吹8級烈風的字眼，更首次表明離岸吹10級暴風。<br />\n而因山竹可能剷上菲律賓，天文台則稍為調弱其掠港時的中心風力，由原先預計的時速220公里，減至205公里，但仍相當強勁。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：打唔正即係無事"},{"pid":"ba23a25437c8c06985ca33f99ce3caf6f049f4a9","tid":817333,"uid":58071,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cb24651e5d41cc46c873dfb0027fb031b81b0d8","tid":817333,"uid":5006,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"Btw 菲律賓今次會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁勁兜野打落去 北部真係渣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9082f478aaab7898bfeb96e95fe00622ea9e92ef","tid":817333,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:12:28.000Z","msg":"燈走咗啦"},{"pid":"85a82ed88295e19bcb6c2d37fa94a61994609c79","tid":817333,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0